{
  "id": "ragChatbot08",
  "meta": {
    "instanceId": "REPLACE_WITH_INSTANCE_ID",
    "templateCredsSetupCompleted": false
  },
  "name": "RAG-Powered Internal Knowledge Chatbot",
  "tags": [
    "client-project",
    "ai-automation",
    "knowledge-base"
  ],
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
      "name": "Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -600,
        -460
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 760,
        "height": 700,
        "content": "## 📚 RAG-Powered Internal Knowledge Chatbot\n\nCompany docs from Notion and Drive sync into a vector store every night. A Slack mention triggers retrieval, and an LLM answers with a source link attached. New docs index automatically, so answers stay current with zero manual updates.\n\n## Two independent flows in this workflow\n1. **Nightly Index Sync** (Schedule, 2am) → pulls Notion pages + Drive files → chunks + embeds → upserts into Pinecone.\n2. **Slack Q&A** (Slack Trigger, app_mention) → AI Agent retrieves from Pinecone and replies in-thread with a source link.\n\n## Setup (about 25 minutes)\n1. Connect Notion, Google Drive, OpenAI and Pinecone credentials.\n2. Set your Pinecone index name in both *Pinecone: Insert Docs* and *Knowledge Base (RAG Tool)*.\n3. Connect Slack and enable the `app_mention` event on the Slack app, scoped to your #ask-docs channel."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
      "name": "Nightly Sync (2am)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "position": [
        -200,
        -160
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "days",
              "daysInterval": 1,
              "triggerAtHour": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 1.2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
      "name": "Search Notion Pages",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.notion",
      "position": [
        40,
        -260
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "page",
        "operation": "search",
        "text": "",
        "returnAll": true,
        "options": {
          "sort": {
            "sortValue": {
              "direction": "descending",
              "timestamp": "last_edited_time"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "credentials": {
        "notionApi": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Notion account"
        }
      },
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 2,
      "typeVersion": 2.2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
      "name": "Search Drive Files",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive",
      "position": [
        40,
        -60
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "fileFolder",
        "operation": "search",
        "searchMethod": "query",
        "returnAll": true,
        "filter": {
          "whatToSearch": "files"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "credentials": {
        "googleDriveOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Google Drive account"
        }
      },
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 2,
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
      "name": "Combine Doc Sources",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.merge",
      "position": [
        280,
        -160
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "combine",
        "combineBy": "combineAll",
        "numberInputs": 2,
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 3.2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006",
      "name": "Normalize Doc List",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "position": [
        500,
        -160
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const notionDocs = $('Search Notion Pages').all().map(i => ({ id: i.json.id, title: i.json.name || 'Untitled', url: i.json.url, source: 'notion' }));\nconst driveDocs = $('Search Drive Files').all().map(i => ({ id: i.json.id, title: i.json.name, url: `https://drive.google.com/file/d/${i.json.id}/view`, source: 'drive' }));\nreturn [...notionDocs, ...driveDocs].map(d => ({ json: d }));"
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007",
      "name": "Process Each Doc",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "position": [
        720,
        -160
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1,
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008",
      "name": "Sync Done",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.noOp",
      "position": [
        960,
        -300
      ],
      "parameters": {},
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000009",
      "name": "Is Notion Doc?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "position": [
        960,
        -100
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "options": {},
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "version": 1,
            "leftValue": "",
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose"
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-is-notion",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              },
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.source }}",
              "rightValue": "notion"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 2.2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000a",
      "name": "Get Notion Page Blocks",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.notion",
      "position": [
        1200,
        -220
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "block",
        "operation": "getAll",
        "blockId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "id",
          "value": "={{ $json.id }}"
        },
        "returnAll": true
      },
      "credentials": {
        "notionApi": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Notion account"
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 2.2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000b",
      "name": "Flatten Notion Text",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "position": [
        1440,
        -220
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const doc = $('Process Each Doc').item.json;\nconst text = $input.all().map(b => b.json.text || '').filter(Boolean).join('\\n');\nreturn [{ json: { id: doc.id, title: doc.title, url: doc.url, source: doc.source, content: text || doc.title } }];"
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000c",
      "name": "Download Drive File",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive",
      "position": [
        1200,
        40
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "file",
        "operation": "download",
        "fileId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "id",
          "value": "={{ $json.id }}"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "credentials": {
        "googleDriveOAuth2Api": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Google Drive account"
        }
      },
      "continueOnFail": true,
      "typeVersion": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000d",
      "name": "Extract Drive Text",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.extractFromFile",
      "position": [
        1440,
        40
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "text",
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 1.1
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000e",
      "name": "Build Drive Doc",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "position": [
        1680,
        40
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const doc = $('Process Each Doc').item.json;\nreturn [{ json: { id: doc.id, title: doc.title, url: doc.url, source: doc.source, content: $json.data || doc.title } }];"
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "k0000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000000f",
      "name": "Pinecone: Insert Docs",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.vectorStorePinecone",
      "position": [
        1920,
        -100
